    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Surgeon 1581 .338 LM",
      "en": "Surgeon 1581 .338 LM"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "由Surgeon Rifles制造的Surgeon 1581加长枪机采用整块钢坯精密加工而成，配备一体化20 MOA导轨和后坐凸耳。该枪机基于雷明顿700标准设计，兼容雷明顿700扳机组，可适配大多数为雷明顿700设计的枪托和机匣接口。",
      "en": "Manufactured by Surgeon Rifles, the Surgeon 1581 Long Action is machined from a solid piece of billet steel and comes with equipped with an integral 20 MOA rail and recoil lug. Based off of the Remington 700 footprint, the Surgeon 1581 works with Remington 700 triggers and fits in most stocks and chassis inlet for the Remington 700."
    },
